      content: `<p>FERSUTER SL (company owner of the registered trademark SPORTSMATCH), in application of current regulations on personal data protection, informs that the personal data collected through the forms on the SPORTSMATCH.PRO website, are included in the automated files specific to users of FERSUTER SL services.</p>

